prefuse.visual

Interface NodeItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Node, Tuple, VisualItem
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TableNodeItem

    public interface NodeItem
extends VisualItem, Node
    VisualItem that represents a node in a graph. This interface combines the VisualItem interface with the Node interface.
